Maury Sterling https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maury_Sterling 0 Charles Maury Wallace Sterling (born September 1, 1971) is an American actor. He is best known for playing Max in Homeland, Rafferty in the comedy film Beverly Hills Chihuahua and Lester Tremor in the action film Smokin' Aces.
